    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662480/extras/c10279545d5a55520530d9f3cb511b4c.poster.avif?t=1726826799\" width=610 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662480/extras/c10279545d5a55520530d9f3cb511b4c.webm?t=1726826799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662480/extras/c10279545d5a55520530d9f3cb511b4c.mp4?t=1726826799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662480/extras/36935a3f74e2b15fdcd59ed81bcdb1c8.webp?t=1726826799\" width=616 height=32 /></span><br><br>&quot;整个世界一片火海。<br><br>倒也没有那么恐怖，不过这个区域已经完全被大火吞噬。<br><br>你作为训练有素的消防人员，肩负调查事故原因与搜救人员的使命，即将降落进入这个烈焰地狱。不过，你将发现一处不明军用场所，你的行动计划将因此受到干扰。&quot;<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662480/extras/c10279545d5a55520530d9f3cb511b4c.poster.avif?t=1726826799\" width=610 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662480/extras/c10279545d5a55520530d9f3cb511b4c.webm?t=1726826799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662480/extras/c10279545d5a55520530d9f3cb511b4c.mp4?t=1726826799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>由《死亡细胞》的前制作人员为您献上一款独一无二的2D消防游戏。真正的消防员，敢于直面回燃、爆炸的墙壁和消防水管。</strong><br></li><li> 该游戏流程简短，品质优良。<br></li><li> 拿起消防水管，控制火情，深入火灾现场。<br></li><li>不是肉鸽，胜似肉鸽，还等什么，快来玩吧！</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662480/extras/f7211d8847b51158e1506f3902069a76.webp?t=1726826799\" width=616 height=32 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662480/extras/4828af579b79a0bd613f7752e541be92.avif?t=1726826799\" width=616 height=170 /></span><br><br>为致敬《Celeste》，《Nuclear Blaze》也为玩家提供了难度调节的选项。该游戏没有简单或困难模式，不过你可以手动将默认难度设置视为相当困难。<br><br><strong>不用刻意为难自己。玩游戏，就是为了开心。.</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662480/extras/a003908e33c8b38022e22bcec650c167.webp?t=1726826799\" width=616 height=32 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662480/extras/f5ab6e39474d61fd1963f5bba5b8bf66.avif?t=1726826799\" width=616 height=180 /></span><br><br>《Nuclear Blaze》最早是我在 Ludum Dare Game Jam 活动的参赛作品。该游戏的创作时间仅有48小时，却在之后收获了大量积极反馈和支持 :)<br>当时，我那年仅三岁的儿子特别喜欢消防员。这个游戏本来是想做给他的，结果我越做越复杂。最后，这款游戏的难度完全超过了他能接受的程度，因此我特地追加了这个“儿童模式”。<br>儿童模式是这款游戏的特殊模式，主要包含以下规则：<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>简单关卡<br></li><li>无限生命<br></li><li>无限水量<br></li><li>自动瞄准<br></li><li>简约键位<br></li><li>深受小玩家们喜爱的卡车和直升机。</li></ul>",
